Sorry I couldn't RP till now, but I was busy celbrating my birthday.

::Zardus::

Zardus lands at the designated meeting place. It was night and a storm was 
starting. Lightning lit up the area, outlining Zardus' black form against the 
sky, his red optics making him look like a creature straight from the very 
bottom of the pit.

He looks around, waiting for the others to get there.
